    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to see this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for a new home. This car has been my absolute pride and joy\u2014it\u2019s in incredible shape and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, keeping it spotless and strictly following every service check. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for an adventure, you\u2019ve found it. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 43900.0,
