    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts its original deep-luster paint, free of any swirl marks, chips, or imperfections, and has been protected by a high-end ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh state; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the original carpets have been protected by weather-proof mats since the first mile. Mechanically, it is flawless. It has been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy, including a documented history of every fluid flush and inspection. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage shows no signs of road wear. This is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did when it first rolled off the assembly line. All original manuals, keys, and service records are included.",
      "price": 44800.0,
